### 4. **KEY PATTERNS & ARCHITECTURE**

#### **Render Mode Pattern:**
- `@rendermode InteractiveServer` - Used for interactive pages (Counter, Home Dashboard)
- No rendermode - Rendered statically (Auth, Weather)
- `@attribute [StreamRendering]` - Used for streaming data (Weather)

#### **Dependency Injection Pattern:**
```csharp
@inject PatientService PatientService
@inject AppointmentService AppointmentService
@inject BillingService BillingService
```

#### **Authorization Attributes:**
```csharp
@attribute [Authorize]  // Requires authentication
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization
```

#### **Navigation Pattern:**
- Used in NavMenu.razor with `<NavLink>` components
- Links: Dashboard ("/"), Patients ("patients"), Appointments ("appointments"), Billing ("billing")

#### **Service Pattern - Search/Filter:**
All services implement similar patterns:
```csharp
public async Task<List<T>> GetXAsync(string? search = null)
{
    var query = db.Items.Include(...).AsQueryable();

    if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(search))
    {
        var term = search.Trim().ToLower();
        query = query.Where(/* case-insensitive contains search */);
    }

    return await query.OrderBy(...).ToListAsync();
}
```

#### **CRUD Pattern in Services:**
- `SaveAsync()` - Create or Update based on `Id == 0`
- `DeleteAsync()` - Async delete with null check
- `GetAsync(id)` - Single item with related data
- `GetListAsync()` - List with optional search

#### **Database Context Pattern:**
```csharp
public class ApplicationDbContext(DbContextOptions<ApplicationDbContext> options) 
    : IdentityDbContext<ApplicationUser>(options)
{
    public DbSet<Owner> Owners => Set<Owner>();
    public DbSet<Pet> Pets => Set<Pet>();
    // ... includes relationship configuration in OnModelCreating
}
```

#### **Data Annotations Used:**
- `[Required]` - Required fields
- `[MaxLength(n)]` - String length validation
- `[Range(min, max)]` - Numeric/decimal ranges
- `[EmailAddress]` - Email validation
- `[Phone]` - Phone validation
- `[StreamRendering]` - Stream content rendering

#### **Computed Properties Pattern:**
```csharp
public decimal Total => Items.Sum(i => i.Amount);
public decimal Balance => Total - AmountPaid;
public DateTime EndTime => StartTime.AddMinutes(DurationMinutes);
```

